                  </persName>
                  <rs id="t18430821-2323-offence-2" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18430821-2323-offence-2" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18430821-2323-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>, for feloniously receiving the same, well knowing them to have been stolen; against the Statute, &amp;c.</rs>
