                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I knew the house four doors down Rose-lane—it is now pulled down.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. WILDE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Did not Clifford tell you the bag had been left for Mr. Samson? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I know Samson lives in Fashion-street—I do not know where he is—I have not looked after him.</p>
